## Estrutura de Pastas

```
app/
├── components/
│   ├── atoms/       # UButton wraps, ícones customizados, badges
│   ├── molecules/   # StatCard, SearchInput, UserMenu
│   ├── organisms/   # AppSidebar, AppHeader, DataTable, FormPanel
│   └── templates/   # DashboardLayout, AuthLayout
├── composables/     # useAuth, useTable, useDashboard
├── pages/           # index.vue, users/index.vue, settings.vue
├── layouts/         # default.vue, auth.vue
└── types/           # index.ts (interfaces e enums)
```

---

## Componentes Nuxt UI — Mapa de Uso

| Categoria  | Componentes                                                                 |
|------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Layout     | `UDashboardLayout`, `UDashboardPanel`, `UMain`, `UContainer`               |
| Sidebar    | `USidebar` — responsivo, fixo no desktop, vira Modal/Slideover/Drawer no mobile. Variantes: `sidebar`, `floating`, `inset`. Modos: `offcanvas`, `icon`, `none` |
| Navegação  | `UNavigationLinks`, `UNavigationMenu`, `UBreadcrumb`                        |
| Dados      | `UTable`, `UPagination`                                                     |
| Formulários| `UForm`, `UFormField`, `UInput`, `USelect`, `UCheckbox`, `UTextarea`, `USwitch` |
| Feedback   | `UAlert`, `UToast`, `UProgress`, `USkeleton`                                |
| Overlay    | `UModal`, `UDrawer`, `UPopover`, `UDropdownMenu`, `UTooltip`                |
| Elementos  | `UButton`, `UBadge`, `UAvatar`, `UCard`, `UIcon`, `UChip`, `USeparator`    |
| Chat / AI  | `UChatMessages`, `UChatReasoning`, `UChatTool`, `UChatShimmer`              |
| Misc       | `UCommandPalette`, `UColorModeButton`, `UColorModeToggle`                   |

