## USidebar — Uso Correto (v4.6+)

```vue
<!-- components/organisms/AppSidebar.vue -->
<template>
  <USidebar v-model:open="open" collapsible="icon">
    <template #header>
      <NuxtLink to="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3">
        <UIcon name="i-lucide-zap" class="size-6 text-(--ui-primary)" />
        <span class="font-semibold text-(--ui-text)">MyApp</span>
      </NuxtLink>
    </template>

    <UNavigationLinks :items="links" />

    <template #footer>
      <UserMenu />
    </template>
  </USidebar>
</template>
```

